<p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>

<p>Running AI models in production requires the right infrastructure. Whether you're deploying a fine-tuned LLM as an API, running Stable Diffusion inference at scale, training custom models, or serving embeddings for a RAG pipeline — your choice of VPS or cloud GPU provider directly impacts performance, cost, and developer experience.</p>

<p>We evaluated the top VPS and cloud GPU providers for AI workloads in 2026, comparing GPU options, pricing models, global coverage, ease of use, and ecosystem integration. Here's what we found.</p>

